column5: ####o, I'm heading up to Atikokan, Ontario in a few weeks and I'm hoping to find some lake maps before then. I'm looking for hydrographic maps showing the depths. Do you think anything like this will be availible. Where should I look? Thanks!

[font color=green size=3][b] Unless you are going to a large and popular body of water, there is a very small chance of finding hydrographic maps. If they exist you likely would likely find them locally, a baitshop, or convience store would be a good place to look. Good luck
